# Python
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/venv
**/.venv

# Node
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.npm

# Dev files
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/start.bat
**/setup.bat
**/*.log
**/*.zip

# Secrets -- injected at container runtime via docker-compose's env_file: .env,
# never baked into the image. Explicitly excluded here so `COPY backend/ ./backend/`
# and similar steps can never accidentally bundle it into an image layer.
.env
**/.env

# IDE
**/.vscode
**/.idea
